Liv Rundgren Tyler -LRB- born Liv Rundgren ; July 1 , 1977 -RRB- is an American actress and former model .
She is the daughter of Aerosmith 's lead singer , Steven Tyler , and model Bebe Buell .
Tyler began a career in modeling at the age of 14 but , after less than a year , she decided to focus on acting .
